title: 'Never expected this from amazon.'
body: This is the for first time i have got delivered such faulty promises from.amazon/seller . The packet contains 10 pencils as u can see i got only 7 pencils..3 r missing..the outer packaging is fine but the pencil box itself is tampered in such a way that..its not professional u kno. We shop here with outmost trust and confidence. And in the end i was not expecting this.  Seller shouldn't have done this to any customer its questions our trust towards both the seller and the product. .please i request amazon to look up at this matter as soon as possible.
